Class AvailabilitySetUpdate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute.UpdateResource
      • com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute.AvailabilitySetUpdate

  • public class AvailabilitySetUpdate
extends UpdateResource
    Specifies information about the availability set that the virtual machine should be assigned to. Only tags may be updated.
